                        <div id="collapse1Three4" class="accordion-body collapse">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>With proper design and installation following industry best practices, your roof should maintain all its pre-solar integrity. MNRE Authorized Installers performs best practices so that you can rest easy knowing that your roof will be okay. Be sure to ask your installer about any guarantees they offer on their installation quality.</p>
