                                </a>
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapse1five4" class="accordion-body collapse">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>Yes. A general rule of thumb is that if you can clearly see your solar panels, they can produce electricity. In fact, given equal sunlight, a solar panel on a cold day will out-produce a solar panel on a hot day.</p>
                            </div>
