                        <div id="collapse1One6" class="accordion-body collapse in">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>For the safety of workers attempting to fix power outages, solar PV systems that are connected to the electrical grid are required by utility regulations to shut off during blackouts or shutdowns. <br><br>AHA Rooftop Solar Helper recommends battery backup or traditional generators in places where blackouts occur regularly </p>
